Aristarchus Scoping Rules:

(define-body identifier expr expr) | binds identifier in the program, but not inside of the define.

(define-satellite identifier expr) | binds identifier in the program, but not inside of the define.

(define-connection identifier expr expr expr) | binds identifier in the program, but not inside of the define.

(define-system identifier expr expr ...) | binds idetntifier in the program, but not inside of the define.


